    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/90?text=LOGO" alt="Company Logo" style="border-radius: 50%;">
        </div>
        <h1>Office of the CISO</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="banner">
        <p>IT Security Team: Official inquiry and update regarding your workstations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body-text">
        <p>Hi [Employee Name],</p>

        <p>It was great seeing you and your team at the regional campus retreat last weekend. Go Wildcats! Returning the favor from our last project together, I wanted to personally make sure your department is looped in on this before the general rollout.</p>

